he wanted to spare my feelings.

1247
01:44:13,843 --> 01:44:19,156
"He's a withdrawn and primitive man,"

1248
01:44:21,809 --> 01:44:26,979
but at heart he's loyal
and he is good.

1249
01:44:26,980 --> 01:44:30,417
What do you want with my husband?

1250
