I don't want anything with
your husband or anybody.

1251
01:44:41,036 --> 01:44:43,805
What about Tom and the hand-holding
at the picnic?

1252
01:44:44,330 --> 01:44:46,808
That's different. I like Tom.

1253
01:44:48,543 --> 01:44:50,794
But you don't like Chuck.

1254
01:44:50,795 --> 01:44:53,726
"Liz and Martha are behind me,
when I tell you..."

1255
01:44:53,727 --> 01:44:56,467
