to teach you a lesson."

1256
01:44:56,468 --> 01:44:59,278
I believe in education.

1257
01:45:03,140 --> 01:45:04,040
Vera!

1258
01:45:04,141 --> 01:45:09,288
No. I believe smashing them is
less a crime than making them.

1259
01:45:11,064 --> 01:45:15,168
Vera.. remember how I
taught your children..

1260
01:45:15,193 --> 01:45:16,173
"What?"

1261
01:45:16,174 --> 01:45:19,182
"Remember how happy
you were, when I..."

1262
01:45:19,239 --> 01:45:20,188
When you what?

1263
01:45:20,189 --> 01:45:23,075
