human tissue disintegrating.

1274
01:46:23,467 --> 01:46:28,322
The figurines were the offspring of the
meeting between the township and her.

1275
01:46:28,430 --> 01:46:31,899
"They were the proof
that in spite of everything,"

1276
01:46:31,900 --> 01:46:35,255
