1278
01:46:39,775 --> 01:46:45,422
"For the first time since her childhood,
she wept."

1279
01:47:14,767 --> 01:47:18,283
"Grace went to see Tom that very night,
and informed him..."

1280
01:47:18,284 --> 01:47:22,175
