that I will pay him back.

1294
01:48:09,110 --> 01:48:10,629
Of course.

1295
01:48:15,242 --> 01:48:16,467
Thank you.

1296
01:48:19,954 --> 01:48:23,516
You are always rescuing me.

1297
01:48:27,212 --> 01:48:30,439
I can't believe that you go on
being there for me.

1298
01:48:33,135 --> 01:48:34,277
Good night..

1299
01:48:37,346 --> 01:48:38,989
You should get some sleep.

1300
01:48:48,106 --> 01:48:51,042
Grace went to see Ben next morning.

1301
01:48:55,239 --> 01:48:59,117
"When Grace presented the payment
as compensation between friends,"

1302
01:48:59,118 --> 01:49:01,577
"Ben did not object too heartily,"

1303
01:49:01,578 --> 01:49:05,297
considering the trouble he could receive
from the rest of the towns-people

1304
01:49:05,298 --> 01:49:07,276
when they realized
what had happened.

1305
01:49:07,333 --> 01:49:10,770
"Perhaps they'd all be relieved
that she was out of their lives,"

1306
01:49:11,087 --> 01:49:14,648
but somehow
Grace wasn't too sure of that.

1307
01:49:15,175 --> 01:49:16,863
"Ben agreed to drive her"

1308
01:49:16,864 --> 01:49:21,888
"even though he wasn't out to profit from
other folks' misfortunes, as he put it."

1309
01:49:21,889 --> 01:49:24,933
I don't wanna profit from
other folks' misfortunes.

1310
01:49:24,934 --> 01:49:26,017
No...

1311
01:49:26,018 --> 01:49:27,207
