1312
01:49:27,208 --> 01:49:30,841
that Ben would have driven to the gates
of Hell and back for ten dollars

1313
01:49:30,981 --> 01:49:35,193
And the criminal aspect bugged him less
than Grace would ever have guessed;

1314
01:49:35,194 --> 01:49:38,713
He had freighted all kinds of things
in his day.

1315
01:49:39,030 --> 01:49:42,634
The plan was for Grace to hide
among the apples.

1316
01:49:42,659 --> 01:49:47,763
"Knowing the exact time to harvest is the
greatest art of all, Chuck had said,"

1317
01:49:47,872 --> 01:49:52,834
and the time had come
for the apples and for Grace.

1318
01:49:52,835 --> 01:49:54,937
"Grace, where 've you been?"

1319
01:49:54,962 --> 01:49:56,670
If I'd displayed the same indifference

1320
01:49:56,671 --> 01:49:58,965
