01:50:05,140 --> 01:50:06,573
June is near to bursting.

1324
01:50:06,598 --> 01:50:09,267
"She can't use the pot on her own,
as you well know."

1325
01:50:09,268 --> 01:50:10,755
It ain't fittin' to toy with her...

1326
01:50:10,756 --> 01:50:13,256
just 'cause she's crippled
and can't help herself.

